plot patient visits against visit_med75

plot_visit_med75.Rd

plots cumulative AEs against visits for patients at sites of given study and compares against visit_med75.

plot_visit_med75(df_visit, df_site, study_roche_str, n_sites = 6)

Arguments

df_visit

dataframe
df_site

dataframe, as returned by site_aggr()
study_roche_str

character, specify study in study_roche column
n_sites

integer, Default: 6

Value

ggplot

Details

""

Examples

df_visit <- boot_sim_test_data_study(n_pat = 120, n_sites = 6,
    frac_site_with_ur = 0.4, ur_rate = 0.6)

df_visit$study_roche <- "A"
df_site <- site_aggr(df_visit)

plot_visit_med75(df_visit, df_site, study_roche_str = "A", n_site = 6)
